title: Rylan Clark-Neal tells Holly Willoughby she 'looks dirty like a Page 3 model' on This Morning
text:

Holly Willoughby was pretty offended by Rylan Clark-Neal on This Morning today, when he told her she looked “dirty”, “like a Page 3 model”. 
The ITV daytime host was laughing with her co-host Phillip Schofield and the Celebrity Big Brother Bit On The Side host when they came back from a break. 
And Phillip revealed it was because Rylan had just “watched him digging a big hole” by accidentally blasting Holly’s look. 
Holly was wearing a white shirt printed with rainbows on it today. Read More Rylan said Holly looked dirty (Photo: ITV) Holly was pretty offended (Photo: ITV) Phil found it hilarious (Photo: ITV) 
And Rylan explained: “I just said you look dirty!” 
Backtracking, he added: “You look beautiful though! 
“You look like a Page 3 model – in a nice way. 
“I’d want to look like that if I were a girl.” 
Phil couldn’t control his laughter, and told Rylan he was “turning into Kim Woodburn”! Read More Rylan kept digging a hole (Photo: ITV) Holly just wasn't impressed (Photo: ITV) 
Rylan then launched into an incredible impression of the Celebrity Big Brother star. 
And he added to Holly: “You look beautiful, lovely!”
